description: All of the crepes at Sweet n Savory in Louisville, KY are gluten and dairy free as well as made with local, free-range eggs. As much local meats, cheese, fruits, and vegetables as possible are also incorporated so show your community support by eating something sweet or savory here! The fresh fruit smoothies are made entirely with real fruit and fruit juices and no ice or artificial additives. Customers have the option to enhance their smoothie with a protein, vitamin, and antioxidant supplement giving them a low fat, low calorie, healthy meal replacement option. Also available is delicious, creamy gelato, which makes a perfectly refreshing summer treat so come grab a scoop!
name: Sweet n Savory
